    top: 60,
    right: 100,
    bottom: 40,
    left: 90
  };
  var width = 600 - margin.left - margin.right;
  var height = 400 - margin.top - margin.bottom;

  var svg = d3.select("#chartContainer1").append("svg").attr("width", width + margin.left + margin.right + 300).attr("height", height + margin.top + margin.bottom + 100).append("g").attr("transform", "translate(".concat(margin.left, ",").concat(margin.top, ")"));
  var xMin = d3.min(filteredData1, function (d) {
    return d.views;
  });
  var xMax = d3.max(filteredData1, function (d) {
    return d.views;
  });
  var yMin = d3.min(filteredData1, function (d) {
    return d.income;
  });
  var yMax = d3.max(filteredData1, function (d) {
    return d.income;
  });
  var xScale = d3.scaleLog().domain([xMin, xMax]).range([0, width]);
  var yScale = d3.scaleLog().domain([yMin, yMax]).range([height, 0]);
  var color = d3.scaleOrdinal(d3.schemeCategory10);
  svg.selectAll(".dot").data(filteredData1).enter().append("circle").attr("class", "dot").attr("cx", function (d) {
    return xScale(d.views);
  }).attr("cy", function (d) {
    return yScale(d.income);
  }).attr("r", 2).style("fill", function (d) {
    return color(d.category);
  });

  svg.append("text").attr("x", -margin.left + 60).attr("y", -height / 2 + 120).attr("dy", "1em").style("font-size", "12px") // 设置字体大小为 12px
  .attr("text-anchor", "middle").text("年收入/美元");

  legend.append("rect").attr("x", width - 18).attr("width", 18).attr("height", 18).style("fill", color);
